WESTERN SOUTH ATLANTIC.
URUGUAY.
1. SEISMIC SURVEY 30 AND 31 OCT BY M/V RAMFORM VANGUARD TOWING 12
   7000 METER LONG CABLES ALONG TRACKLINES BETWEEN:
   A. 35-21.78S 052-12.02W AND 36-15.63S 053-06.07W.
   B. 36-02.92S 053-04.53W AND 35-15.88S 052-17.40W.
   NINE MILE BERTH REQUESTED.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 01 NOV 13.
